{
  "stem": "894.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were about, uh-- I believe there were about 50,000 people, and there were about 12,000 to 15,000 Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very-- a lot of Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I looked up in the and it tells you that the first settlers were there in the 1700s, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very slowly they trickled in, and it became like a very nice, nice heimische town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because the parents were born in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my mother never learned Romanian, because she just spoke Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we went to-- to Romanian school, the teachers would threaten us, because the students were always speaking Hungarian to each other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they just wanted you to speak Romanian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was a custom, really, to speak mostly Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it had been a Hungarian city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, since I was young, and I wasn't very involved in politics, or interested in it, but what I overheard would have been, let's say, about a year or two earlier before they took us away, in 1944, because they listened to radio, and they heard, and people came from Poland.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when Hitler went into Poland, a lot of the people escaped to Hungary, hoping to escape-- you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew that there is a lot of problems, that people are in ghettos.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I remember hearing that people are being taken away, and that they are hungry, and that they are-- I mean, terrible stories that I overheard.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I know that my mother was absolutely very worried.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember my father expressing concern.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure he was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, being the almost holy man that he was, I guess he just relied on the fact that God will help us.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
